Comment: Oliver, overall you played an excellent game.  I will make some comments.
This wasn't the best move, but just to take you out of book.  Better move would be any of a few Bishop moves, such as a fianchetto, Bb4, etc.  This is not a suicidal move, just not the best.

But from the time you gave me control over this file, you will note that you lose the use of your Queen for the rest of the game.
